---
By: Dalai Lama
Source:
  URL: https://twitter.com/DalaiLama/status/998497410199437312
  Locus:
    Date: 21 May 2018
---
I’m Tibetan, I’m Buddhist and I’m the Dalai Lama, but if I
emphasize these differences it sets me apart and raises barriers with
other people. What we need to do is to pay more attention to the ways in
which we are the same as other people.
